  "title": "3-6 Months Temp Medical Technologist #HGAT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours: </strong></p><ul><li>Can opt for 2 shifts, any 5 days – until 9pm OR 3 shifts, any 5 days of the week</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform routine and specialized tests on patient specimens to support diagnosis and treatment.</li><li>Operate and maintain laboratory instruments, ensuring accurate and reliable results.</li><li>Monitor quality control and adhere to safety and regulatory standards.</li><li>Record, analyze, and promptly communicate test results to medical staff.</li><li>Participate in continuous learning to keep up with advancements in laboratory technology.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Biomedical Science, Microbiology, or related field.</li><li>Detail-oriented with strong analytical skills.</li><li>Flexible to work shifts as scheduled.</li></ul><p><strong>Interested Applications, Please send a detailed resume with photo attach to pharma@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong><br /><strong>Please state your expected salary and reason for leaving for all previous employments. </strong><br /><strong> </strong><br /><strong> Ann Goh Xin Ting</strong></p><p><strong>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</strong><br /><strong>R1875289</strong><br /><strong>E.A License: 99C4599</strong></p>",
